name: Intergalactic Genesis: Mars & Venus, The Voyage of Life. Launched to Space by Uplift Aeros

metadata.name: Venus by Chad Knight #1/11
metadata.description:
**Venus by Chad Knight** - The ethereal and graceful depiction of the cosmic woman.

Born of the sea, **this goddess of love** and beauty points upwards to the planet, radiating inner **strength and resilience** with every curve of her form.

Her silver figure stands **tall and proud**, a symbol of hope and inspiration for all those who yearn **to reach for the stars.**
